{
  "title":"BPOD",
  "date":"2005-01-15 CST",
  "origin":"Funny Logic",
  "url":"text-bpod",
  "author":"Ryan X. Charles"
}



			
				<p>&#8220;This is the bottomless pit of doom,&#8221; he said, as if it were the only one. &#8220;Don&#8217;t ever go in there.&#8221;</p>

	<p>We were in the hallway, and the label on the door said &#8220;BPOD.&#8221; I had no reason to suspect he was lying. He then proceeded to undress, revealing swim trunks beneath his pants. He went in and closed the door, and I never saw him again.</p>

	<p>I spent the rest of the day looking out of various windows.</p>

		
		

